      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR BELLA ROSE (5) has gone well at her last couple of runs here, most recently when second beaten a nose (20.03). Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Good form should continue. CABAO MARBLE (1) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5 lengths into third (19.95) at this track in a Other over 342m. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Winning chance. SAILAWAY BUDDY (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for five wins and two minors. Was out of the placings last time (23.34) at Gawler in a Other, finishing fourth and beaten 4.5 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. SWITCHING LANES (8) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
